.TH JIRA 1 "2025-11-24" "Project Chronos 2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jira \- Jira ticket management CLI tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B jira
[\fIOPTION\fR]
.I COMMAND
[\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B jira
provides full CRUD operations for managing Jira tickets from the command line.
Supports creating, reading, updating, deleting, and listing tickets with rich terminal formatting.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B create
Create a new Jira ticket
.TP
.B read
Read ticket details
.TP
.B update
Update an existing ticket
.TP
.B delete
Delete a ticket
.TP
.B list
List tickets in the project
.TP
.B next-id
Get the next available ticket ID
.SH CREATE OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-summary " " \fISUMMARY\fR
Ticket summary (required). Use Conventional Commits format: type(scope): description
.TP
.BR \-\-description " " \fIDESCRIPTION\fR
Detailed ticket description in markdown format
.TP
.BR \-\-type " " \fITYPE\fR
Issue type: Story, Task, Bug, Epic (default: Story)
.TP
.BR \-\-priority " " \fIPRIORITY\fR
Priority: Low, Medium, High, Critical (default: Medium)
.TP
.BR \-\-labels " " \fILABELS\fR
Comma-separated labels
.TP
.BR \-\-points " " \fIPOINTS\fR
Story points (integer)
.TP
.BR \-\-sprint " " \fISPRINT\fR
Sprint name (default: Sprint 3)
.SH UPDATE OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-summary " " \fISUMMARY\fR
New ticket summary
.TP
.BR \-\-description " " \fIDESCRIPTION\fR
New description
.TP
.BR \-\-status " " \fISTATUS\fR
New status: "To Do", "In Progress", "In Review", "Done"
.TP
.BR \-\-priority " " \fIPRIORITY\fR
New priority
.TP
.BR \-\-points " " \fIPOINTS\fR
Story points
.TP
.BR \-\-labels " " \fILABELS\fR
Comma-separated labels
.SH LIST OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-status " " \fISTATUS\fR
Filter by status
.TP
.BR \-\-limit " " \fILIMIT\fR
Number of results to return (default: 20)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Create a new ticket:
.B jira create
\-\-summary "feat(api): Add user authentication" \-\-description "..." \-\-type Story \-\-priority High
.TP
Read ticket details:
.B jira read
CHRONOS-167
.TP
Update ticket status:
.B jira update
CHRONOS-167 \-\-status "In Progress"
.TP
List recent tickets:
.B jira list
\-\-limit 10
.TP
Delete a ticket:
.B jira delete
CHRONOS-999
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B JIRA_URL
Jira instance URL (e.g., https://automatonicai.atlassian.net)
.TP
.B JIRA_EMAIL
Jira account email
.TP
.B JIRA_API_TOKEN
Jira API token for authentication
.TP
.B JIRA_PROJECT_KEY
Jira project key (default: CHRONOS)
.SH FILES
.TP
.I .env
Environment configuration file
.TP
.I src/chronos/workflows/jira/LAST_TICKET.txt
Tracker file for next ticket ID
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success
.TP
.B 1
Error (authentication, network, or API failure)
